Package: localintel
Type: Package
Title: Local Intelligence - Inequality Mapping Engine for Eurostat and DHS Subnational Indicators
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R: person("Mohamed", "Htitich", 
                  email = "m.ahtitich@outlook.com", 
                  role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8732-6286"))
Description: An inequality mapping engine for fetching, harmonizing, cascading, and
    visualizing subnational indicators from Eurostat (150+ indicators across 14
    thematic domains for 235+ European NUTS-2 regions) and the DHS Program API
    (64+ indicators across 8 domains for 280+ Admin 1 regions in 45+ Sub-Saharan
    African countries). Provides multi-level data cascading with source-level
    tracking, composite scoring, publication-ready maps, AI-generated regional
    insights, and Tableau-ready exports.
